          <h4 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; color: var(--color-primary);">
            Q. 도메인과 호스팅 비용은 포함되나요?
          </h4>
          <p style="color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.7; word-break: keep-all;">
            도메인과 호스팅 비용은 별도입니다. 포함시 별도의 비용이 발생할 수 있습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%= render "shared/tax_partnership_banner" %>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section style="padding: 96px 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00a859, #00d670); color: white;">
  <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2 style="font-size: 40px; font-weight: 800; color: white; margin-bottom: 16px; word-break: keep-all; line-height: 1.3;">
      지금 바로 시작하세요
    </h2>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-bottom: 40px; word-break: keep-all;">
      무료 상담을 통해 최적의 플랜을 추천해드립니다
    </p>
    <%= link_to contact_path, style: "display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 16px 32px; background: white; color: #00a859; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 9999px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);", class: "pricing-cta-btn" do %>
      무료 상담 신청
      <span style="width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 9999px; background: rgba(0, 168, 89, 0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14m-7-7l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </span>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>

